column5: I'm up at steeles and kipling area and white out conditions are passing me and heading right into the GTA with heavy winds. Drive safely!!   Just a heads up!!  dsn
Thanks for the heads up dsn.  Joey
Confucius say: Man who has head up in blizzard has nostrals full of snow.
Ok it cleared up just now. For a moment there I thought ut was going to last.   dsn
Bring on the white stuff!!... And I aint talkin about snow.
